What about the fence for the Quai de Seine / Pont de Sully dog ​​park? It's very nice to have made a wooden fence to hide the poverty during the Olympic games, but small dogs get through it! Several incidents have already occurred, for the safety of our 4-legged friends and that of cyclists, scooters, skateboarders... Please double this fence urgently!

I asked twice for a civil status certificate of my parents' marriage certificate with filiation. I receive a deed from my parents without filiation, can you read it in your department? Do I have to travel to bring you glasses? It is a shame that in 2024 we will have such an incompetent service. So I'm going to start again, hoping that this time someone works correctly. Failing that, I would write directly to the Mayor.

Ms. Hidalgo has implemented a tax on SUVs weighing more than 1,800 kg. As luck would have it, this increase in parking meters only affects German SUVs, the majority of which weigh more than 1800 kg, while their French competitors SUV Peugeot 3008 etc. are just within the weight limit set by the mayor of Paris. I fear that the EU will impose a heavy fine on those who distort competition. I fear that the European Commission will strongly penalize the city of Paris
